### Remover centro de custo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/centros-custo/{{centroCustoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 204 No Content

###

### Remover ID inexistente (deve retornar 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/centros-custo/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 404 Not Found
# {
#   "statusCode": 404,
#   "message": "Centro de custo com ID 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 não encontrado",
#   "error": "Not Found"
# }

###

### Remover com UUID inválido (deve retornar 400)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/centros-custo/invalid-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 400 Bad Request
# {
#   "statusCode": 400,
#   "message": "Validation failed (uuid is expected)",
#   "error": "Bad Request"
# }

###

### Remover sem autenticação (deve falhar)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/centros-custo/{{centroCustoId}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 401 Unauthorized

###
